<p>Speaking of lists, you do not need to list <em>every</em> design software title you know. Itâ€™s enough to state that you are proficient with using them. You can mention that if you excel at one more than others if you specialize in a disciplineâ€”After Effects for motion graphics, for example. Do not claim to be a Photoshop god. Sorry, but youâ€™re likely not one.</p>

